name: Missed Call (qwenty3322)
description:
Warning: Flashing Images ,Loud Noises and Jump Scares Play at your own risk

Also read controls before playing you have been warned.

You woke up at an unkown place,try to find the exit ,But at least you are not alone, There is someone you can talk to and he is trying to help you or thats what he says.

Description

Missed Call is a game where you can make choices that affects the story and how the game works.

max 15 min playtime.

Controls

  • Arrow keys: Move around
  • Z: Interact 
  • X: Exit
  • C: Phone

Oh and there is 0(Zero)

Programs

Game maker studio 2,Paint.net,Bosca ceoil,Audacity
